WEBVTT


00:00:48.350 --> 00:00:52.970
[The Ferry Man: 10th Anniversary]

00:00:53.480 --> 00:00:56.020
[Episode 18]

00:00:57.840 --> 00:00:58.670
Yuhuang...

00:01:02.670 --> 00:01:04.400
It is already past midnight.

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:09.200
Have you forgotten me too?

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:20.560
Yuhuang!

00:01:21.230 --> 00:01:22.000
Shouldn't you

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:23.260
have forgotten me too?

00:01:26.760 --> 00:01:28.640
I have no money left!

00:01:30.950 --> 00:01:31.510
Come on!

00:01:32.310 --> 00:01:33.240
Don't be afraid!

00:01:52.310 --> 00:01:53.240
Don't be afraid!

00:02:14.250 --> 00:02:17.180
When all things reincarnate
through time and space,

00:02:18.150 --> 00:02:19.079
only love

00:02:20.030 --> 00:02:22.520
remains a constant light,

00:02:23.360 --> 00:02:25.000
shining through every form.

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:27.590
Director.

00:02:30.240 --> 00:02:30.800
Xiaoni.

00:02:31.190 --> 00:02:32.250
Whose desk is this?

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:33.870
This desk?

00:02:35.150 --> 00:02:36.150
I can't remember.

00:02:36.360 --> 00:02:37.590
No one is there, I think.

00:02:37.590 --> 00:02:38.920
It's always been empty.

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:41.360
No way.

00:02:41.870 --> 00:02:42.870
Why do I feel like

00:02:43.630 --> 00:02:45.160
we are missing an employee?

00:02:56.870 --> 00:02:58.530
I really don't know anything.

00:02:58.960 --> 00:03:01.360
I really don't know anything!

00:03:03.030 --> 00:03:04.690
I really don't know anything.

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:06.660
I really don't know anything.

00:03:07.080 --> 00:03:07.910
I really...

00:03:11.360 --> 00:03:12.400
Still reading?

00:03:12.870 --> 00:03:14.130
You only have one line.

00:03:15.590 --> 00:03:16.990
Don't strain your voice.

00:03:20.079 --> 00:03:21.079
I've had enough.

00:03:22.150 --> 00:03:23.950
But I can't really say anything.

00:03:24.430 --> 00:03:25.690
What do you want to say?

00:03:27.910 --> 00:03:29.000
This director.

00:03:29.190 --> 00:03:30.240
He is way too slow.

00:03:30.840 --> 00:03:31.590
Right?

00:03:31.960 --> 00:03:32.710
Tell me about it.

00:03:32.710 --> 00:03:34.190
I've been waiting all day.

00:03:34.310 --> 00:03:35.590
It still isn't my scene.

00:03:35.590 --> 00:03:36.710
Doing art?

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:38.600
Does he even know what art is?

00:03:39.840 --> 00:03:40.680
Actually, I think

00:03:40.680 --> 00:03:41.750
I'm perfectly suited to the role

00:03:41.750 --> 00:03:43.910
of Yingtao
in Strange Tales of Tang Dynasty.

00:03:43.910 --> 00:03:45.840
It's a pity I didn't get the chance.

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:47.400
Now I can only be an extra.

00:03:47.630 --> 00:03:48.680
If they let me play it,

00:03:48.680 --> 00:03:50.680
I'd definitely act better than her.

00:03:51.360 --> 00:03:52.960
I'm just not as pretty as her.

00:03:53.750 --> 00:03:55.480
But my acting is better, right?

00:03:55.560 --> 00:03:56.420
Stop dreaming.

00:03:56.870 --> 00:03:58.130
For such a big project,

00:03:58.470 --> 00:03:59.800
we'd never get a chance.

00:04:01.190 --> 00:04:03.250
Stay out of a pretty lady's business!

00:04:07.430 --> 00:04:08.470
What kind of bird is that?

00:04:08.470 --> 00:04:09.930
I've never seen it before.

00:04:10.750 --> 00:04:11.750
Me neither.

00:04:12.910 --> 00:04:13.840
Look at that one.

00:04:14.030 --> 00:04:16.120
It looks like it's wearing a red scarf.

00:04:16.120 --> 00:04:17.180
It must be a female.

00:04:19.070 --> 00:04:21.480
The two of them must be a pair.

00:04:38.600 --> 00:04:39.870
Extras for Strange Tales of Tang Dynasty,

00:04:39.870 --> 00:04:40.530
head to set.

00:04:40.830 --> 00:04:41.960
Let's go. Follow me!

00:04:42.360 --> 00:04:43.190
You two, stop holding hands.

00:04:43.190 --> 00:04:43.600
Stop holding hands.

00:04:43.600 --> 00:04:44.530
Go, go, let's go.

00:04:44.800 --> 00:04:45.480
Why are you holding hands?

00:04:45.480 --> 00:04:46.270
Let's go. Head to set.

00:04:46.270 --> 00:04:47.390
What are you doing? Let go.

00:04:47.390 --> 00:04:48.920
He saw us.

00:04:50.430 --> 00:04:52.090
Why are you using a cute voice?

00:04:53.190 --> 00:04:54.430
None of your business!

00:04:54.430 --> 00:04:55.190
So what?

00:04:55.430 --> 00:04:56.190
Alright.

00:04:56.390 --> 00:04:57.190
What a fake.

00:04:58.070 --> 00:04:58.680
Let's go.

00:04:59.159 --> 00:04:59.890
Time to work.

00:06:50.960 --> 00:06:51.440
Fei.

00:06:54.040 --> 00:06:54.840
What's wrong,

00:06:55.270 --> 00:06:56.220
Lord Fei?

00:06:56.550 --> 00:06:58.560
Something is wrong with the program.

00:06:58.560 --> 00:06:59.680
A character you created

00:06:59.680 --> 00:07:01.080
now has self-awareness.

00:07:01.310 --> 00:07:02.360
It took the liberty

00:07:02.360 --> 00:07:03.890
and changed some settings.

00:07:04.040 --> 00:07:04.920
I know.

00:07:05.750 --> 00:07:06.940
It's just two birds.

00:07:07.190 --> 00:07:08.270
Let them be.

00:07:08.520 --> 00:07:09.160
But this kind of bug

00:07:09.160 --> 00:07:10.560
is a very serious matter.

00:07:10.600 --> 00:07:11.630
He even completely erased

00:07:11.630 --> 00:07:12.600
this woman's

00:07:12.630 --> 00:07:13.740
past experiences

00:07:13.830 --> 00:07:14.830
in the real world.

00:07:16.560 --> 00:07:17.270
Do you think

00:07:18.040 --> 00:07:19.440
Yuhuang is that capable?

00:07:20.240 --> 00:07:21.270
He begged me,

00:07:21.510 --> 00:07:22.240
I helped him,

00:07:22.690 --> 00:07:24.890
and made a beautiful love story happen.

00:07:25.430 --> 00:07:28.090
"Wishing to fly together
like birds in the sky."

00:07:30.190 --> 00:07:31.700
A man so obsessed with love

00:07:31.920 --> 00:07:33.310
truly makes me pity him.

00:07:34.680 --> 00:07:36.940
I don't recommend women being lovesick.

00:07:37.159 --> 00:07:38.360
But men

00:07:38.690 --> 00:07:41.290
should definitely be more obsessed
with love.

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:42.540
This way,

00:07:43.040 --> 00:07:44.150
there would be much less

00:07:44.150 --> 00:07:45.710
conflict in this world.

00:07:51.950 --> 00:07:53.880
You really have too much free time.

00:07:55.580 --> 00:07:56.290
Alright.

00:07:57.600 --> 00:07:58.860
Don't forget our plan.

00:08:08.160 --> 00:08:09.680
What a boring man.

00:08:39.830 --> 00:08:45.170
[Chapter 10: Beast City]

00:08:48.390 --> 00:08:49.510
Today's demonic power value:

00:08:49.510 --> 00:08:50.630
77%.

00:08:50.910 --> 00:08:52.630
Five points for today have been deducted.

00:08:52.630 --> 00:08:53.830
Please get some rest.

00:08:53.840 --> 00:08:56.440
Strike a proper balance
between work and rest.

00:08:56.790 --> 00:08:57.480
Sir,

00:08:58.360 --> 00:08:59.360
I ordered coffee.

00:08:59.720 --> 00:09:00.320
Thank you.

00:09:04.610 --> 00:09:06.070
Is this with an extra shot?

00:09:06.510 --> 00:09:07.390
Sir.

00:09:09.100 --> 00:09:11.440
You have such dark circles
under your eyes.

00:09:11.440 --> 00:09:12.700
Did you not sleep well?

00:09:13.200 --> 00:09:14.360
It's past 10 PM,

00:09:15.150 --> 00:09:16.630
and you still ordered coffee.

00:09:16.630 --> 00:09:17.550
And it's with an extra shot.

00:09:17.550 --> 00:09:18.880
And you ordered 10 cups?

00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:21.180
Is there a problem?

00:09:22.670 --> 00:09:23.530
I want a cup too.

00:09:23.630 --> 00:09:24.830
Extra shot, with ice.

00:09:24.870 --> 00:09:25.870
You are Xu, right?

00:09:27.440 --> 00:09:28.720
Hello, I am Zhao Hengzhi.

00:09:28.720 --> 00:09:30.380
You guys made an appointment?

00:09:31.230 --> 00:09:32.150
Here is your coffee.

00:09:32.150 --> 00:09:33.200
Thank you, thank you.

00:09:33.200 --> 00:09:34.730
Your coffee is really good.

00:09:35.790 --> 00:09:36.750
Welcome to come again.

00:09:36.750 --> 00:09:37.320
Goodbye.

00:09:37.510 --> 00:09:38.040
Goodbye.

00:09:50.670 --> 00:09:52.070
What do you want from him?

00:09:52.270 --> 00:09:53.000
Don't worry.

00:09:53.030 --> 00:09:54.120
Just speak boldly.

00:09:54.480 --> 00:09:57.080
I've seen all kinds of
weird "cows and horses".

00:09:59.200 --> 00:10:00.670
I am a cow,

00:10:01.270 --> 00:10:02.600
not a horse.

00:10:04.080 --> 00:10:05.150
That makes sense.

00:10:05.630 --> 00:10:06.120
Xu,

00:10:06.470 --> 00:10:08.110
there are no customers in the shop anyway.

00:10:08.110 --> 00:10:08.840
How about you

00:10:09.270 --> 00:10:10.730
let him see your true form?

00:10:21.150 --> 00:10:22.040
He is a demon.

00:10:35.150 --> 00:10:36.280
Your coffee is good.

00:10:36.440 --> 00:10:37.440
It's refreshing.

00:10:39.510 --> 00:10:40.270
Didn't you say

00:10:40.270 --> 00:10:41.220
you've seen all kinds

00:10:41.220 --> 00:10:42.280
of cows and horses?

00:10:42.840 --> 00:10:43.510
How could you be scared

00:10:43.510 --> 00:10:44.600
like this?

00:10:44.840 --> 00:10:45.510
Yes, yes.

00:10:45.720 --> 00:10:47.790
I have seen demons.

00:10:47.960 --> 00:10:49.790
But it was so sudden, so I...

00:10:50.200 --> 00:10:50.670
Indeed.

00:10:57.030 --> 00:10:57.840
Well, Xu,

00:10:58.200 --> 00:10:58.730
how about this?

00:10:58.730 --> 00:10:59.670
You should put your human skin mask

00:10:59.670 --> 00:11:00.360
back on.

00:11:00.600 --> 00:11:01.120
Lest

00:11:01.150 --> 00:11:02.150
a customer comes in unexpectedly

00:11:02.150 --> 00:11:03.680
and you scare them to death.

00:11:23.630 --> 00:11:24.690
This is the reward.

00:11:27.000 --> 00:11:28.390
This world is crazy.

00:11:28.720 --> 00:11:31.120
A demon
asking the night watchman for help?

00:11:34.150 --> 00:11:35.750
The fragment of a demon core?

00:11:36.230 --> 00:11:36.910
This is good stuff

00:11:36.910 --> 00:11:38.200
for making spirit paper.

00:11:38.200 --> 00:11:39.530
Is this your demon core?

00:11:39.840 --> 00:11:40.840
How could you bear to part with it?

00:11:40.840 --> 00:11:41.330
Seriously.

00:11:41.330 --> 00:11:42.480
What exactly do you

00:11:42.510 --> 00:11:43.570
need our help with?

00:11:43.910 --> 00:11:45.200
Is it a past life resentment

00:11:45.200 --> 00:11:46.530
or an unfulfilled wish?

00:11:49.790 --> 00:11:50.720
I want to resign.

00:11:50.960 --> 00:11:51.480
Resign?

00:11:52.150 --> 00:11:53.410
Well, you can

00:11:53.440 --> 00:11:54.700
go to your company's HR

00:11:54.870 --> 00:11:56.730
and submit a resignation letter.

00:11:57.200 --> 00:11:58.120
The demon world

00:11:58.360 --> 00:12:00.290
is different from the human world.

00:12:00.360 --> 00:12:01.620
Why do you want to quit?

00:12:01.960 --> 00:12:03.030
I'm too tired.

00:12:04.670 --> 00:12:05.870
I really want to rest,

00:12:07.480 --> 00:12:08.510
even for just one day.

00:12:08.510 --> 00:12:08.910
Wait.

00:12:09.080 --> 00:12:10.410
Don't you have days off?

00:12:11.720 --> 00:12:12.780
Demons don't rest.

00:12:13.080 --> 00:12:14.240
What is your job?

00:12:15.150 --> 00:12:16.670
I'm a programmer,

00:12:17.120 --> 00:12:18.580
working on AI technology.

00:12:18.600 --> 00:12:20.150
Do you provide services for demons?

00:12:20.150 --> 00:12:20.510
Yes.

00:12:21.840 --> 00:12:23.440
And for ordinary humans too.

00:12:23.630 --> 00:12:25.960
Our company has very diverse businesses.

00:12:30.750 --> 00:12:31.210
What...

00:12:31.320 --> 00:12:32.080
What is this?

00:12:32.080 --> 00:12:33.390
This is my employee ID badge.

00:12:33.390 --> 00:12:33.850
This...

00:12:33.960 --> 00:12:35.320
How did you get this in your body?

00:12:35.320 --> 00:12:36.180
Didn't it hurt?

00:12:36.440 --> 00:12:37.630
Blue Blood Tech?

00:12:37.910 --> 00:12:38.910
Do you work there?

00:12:39.200 --> 00:12:39.600
Yes.

00:12:40.120 --> 00:12:41.780
Why does that sound familiar?

00:12:41.910 --> 00:12:43.120
Then do you know

00:12:43.320 --> 00:12:44.360
the thing that brings 2D characters

00:12:44.360 --> 00:12:45.750
into the real world?

00:12:46.840 --> 00:12:48.550
The dimensional integration system?

00:12:48.550 --> 00:12:49.120
Right.

00:12:49.720 --> 00:12:51.320
I don't know much about that.

00:12:51.550 --> 00:12:53.480
It's our company's core business,

00:12:53.600 --> 00:12:55.360
closely monitored by the boss himself.

00:12:55.360 --> 00:12:56.240
I'm just an outsider

00:12:56.240 --> 00:12:58.040
responsible for writing codes.

00:12:58.120 --> 00:12:59.850
I don't have access to that yet.

00:13:00.080 --> 00:13:00.910
But your...

00:13:02.340 --> 00:13:03.320
This ID badge

00:13:03.510 --> 00:13:04.910
is connected to my heart.

00:13:05.360 --> 00:13:06.160
That is to say,

00:13:06.240 --> 00:13:08.210
if I quit,

00:13:08.510 --> 00:13:10.080
run away, or skip work,

00:13:11.750 --> 00:13:13.320
this ID badge can kill me.

00:13:14.790 --> 00:13:16.050
What about being late?

00:13:16.230 --> 00:13:17.600
If I'm late...

00:13:26.790 --> 00:13:27.240
Xu.

00:13:27.260 --> 00:13:28.460
You are hurt?

00:13:30.750 --> 00:13:31.880
I'm going to be late.

00:13:32.750 --> 00:13:34.550
I must hurry back to the company.

00:13:36.100 --> 00:13:37.360
You haven't finished.

00:13:41.150 --> 00:13:42.080
Night Watchman,

00:13:43.150 --> 00:13:44.610
I'll come again next time.

00:13:45.320 --> 00:13:46.080
I beg you

00:13:46.600 --> 00:13:47.600
to use your power

00:13:48.600 --> 00:13:49.800
to remove my ID badge.

00:13:50.080 --> 00:13:50.720
That way,

00:13:51.670 --> 00:13:52.960
I will be free.

00:13:55.240 --> 00:13:56.570
I'm counting on you two.

00:14:07.180 --> 00:14:07.840
What are you looking at

00:14:07.840 --> 00:14:08.870
so intently?

00:14:09.320 --> 00:14:10.980
Don't stuff food up your nose.

00:14:11.120 --> 00:14:12.520
I'm checking something.

00:14:12.720 --> 00:14:13.920
Checking something?

00:14:14.480 --> 00:14:15.940
It's early in the morning.

00:14:15.960 --> 00:14:18.620
You're chatting with a pretty girl,
aren't you?

00:14:25.320 --> 00:14:26.960
The CEO of Blue Blood Tech,

00:14:27.790 --> 00:14:28.670
Situ Fei.

00:14:29.840 --> 00:14:30.670
He is a demon.

00:14:31.670 --> 00:14:32.730
What kind of demon?

00:14:33.360 --> 00:14:35.360
I have to see the real person to know.

00:14:35.910 --> 00:14:37.630
Demons run companies too?

00:14:40.620 --> 00:14:41.510
Since ancient times,

00:14:41.510 --> 00:14:42.320
there have always been

00:14:42.320 --> 00:14:43.580
such demon companies.

00:14:43.630 --> 00:14:45.120
As long as
they don't harm the human world,

00:14:45.120 --> 00:14:46.360
they are allowed to exist.

00:14:46.360 --> 00:14:47.510
Besides, who says

00:14:47.750 --> 00:14:49.950
that this world only belongs to humans?

00:14:49.960 --> 00:14:51.620
Is this still the human world?

00:14:51.720 --> 00:14:53.030
This can totally be called a demon world.

00:14:53.030 --> 00:14:54.600
There's no need to be so argumentative.

00:14:54.600 --> 00:14:55.320
You name is Xia Dongqing.

00:14:55.320 --> 00:14:56.780
Why isn't it Xia Chunqing?

00:14:57.670 --> 00:14:58.960
They need somewhere to go.

00:14:58.960 --> 00:15:00.390
They used to live deep in the mountains

00:15:00.390 --> 00:15:01.240
where few people went,

00:15:01.240 --> 00:15:02.790
but now those places have become cities.

00:15:02.790 --> 00:15:04.450
Where do you expect them to go?

00:15:06.510 --> 00:15:07.080
Yu,

00:15:07.240 --> 00:15:07.790
thank you.

00:15:07.790 --> 00:15:08.360
Otherwise,

00:15:08.360 --> 00:15:10.820
I wouldn't be able
to finish this work today.

00:15:21.200 --> 00:15:22.440
I've thought of a way.

00:15:25.600 --> 00:15:27.730
We should be able to succeed this time.

00:15:29.510 --> 00:15:30.240
Don't worry.

00:15:30.480 --> 00:15:31.030
I know.

00:15:34.150 --> 00:15:35.360
We don't have time.

00:15:40.480 --> 00:15:41.550
I have to hang up.

00:15:42.160 --> 00:15:43.320
I've been away from my desk

00:15:43.320 --> 00:15:44.050
for too long.

00:16:05.200 --> 00:16:06.380
The AI said

00:16:06.480 --> 00:16:07.060
this company,

00:16:07.060 --> 00:16:08.600
besides
the dimensional integration system,

00:16:08.600 --> 00:16:09.750
also has human body technology.

00:16:09.750 --> 00:16:11.440
Its main clients are the wealthy class.

00:16:11.440 --> 00:16:12.440
It transforms demons' abilities

00:16:12.440 --> 00:16:14.000
into various abilities

00:16:14.020 --> 00:16:15.150
that humans can use.

00:16:15.600 --> 00:16:16.120
Some

00:16:16.140 --> 00:16:17.480
are like our spirit paper,

00:16:17.480 --> 00:16:18.880
used as auxiliary tools.

00:16:19.320 --> 00:16:20.150
Others

00:16:20.510 --> 00:16:22.670
can even be implanted into the human body

00:16:22.670 --> 00:16:24.390
to alter genes, making it very profitable.

00:16:24.390 --> 00:16:25.840
Why does a demon

00:16:25.840 --> 00:16:26.550
need to make so much money?

00:16:26.550 --> 00:16:29.270
Maybe if it makes enough money,

00:16:30.030 --> 00:16:31.840
no one will care
if it's a human or a demon,

00:16:31.840 --> 00:16:33.270
and it can live in this world

00:16:33.270 --> 00:16:34.600
without wearing a mask.

00:16:34.840 --> 00:16:35.960
That's impressive.

00:16:35.960 --> 00:16:37.750
Then why does Xu want to resign?

00:16:38.030 --> 00:16:38.750
Xu isn't

00:16:38.840 --> 00:16:40.040
the one making money.

00:16:40.360 --> 00:16:41.550
He's just a worker bee.

00:16:41.550 --> 00:16:42.720
In the demon world,

00:16:43.270 --> 00:16:44.440
there are also exploiters

00:16:44.440 --> 00:16:45.840
and the laboring masses.

00:16:45.870 --> 00:16:47.030
Xu's ID badge

00:16:47.200 --> 00:16:48.460
is his labor contract.

00:16:48.510 --> 00:16:50.030
What kind of employee badge

00:16:50.030 --> 00:16:51.690
embeds itself into the flesh?

00:16:52.200 --> 00:16:54.550
Sometimes the demon world

00:16:55.870 --> 00:16:57.930
is much crueler than the human world.

00:17:31.070 --> 00:17:31.680
